OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The boss of a US firm has been         
OL,6, criticised after he fired around 900 of
OL,7, his staff on a single Zoom call.       
OL,9,F"If you're on this call you're part of 
OL,10,Fthe unlucky group being laid off," said
OL,11,FVishal Garg, chief executive of        
OL,12,Fmortgage firm Better.com, on the call, 
OL,13,Flater uploaded to social media.        
OL,15,FComments on social media said it was   
OL,16,F"cold", "harsh" and "a horrible move", 
OL,17,Fespecially in the run up to Christmas. 
OL,19,F"Last time I did (this) I cried," Mr   
OL,20,FGarg told the staff on the call.       
